FIX: Team Line Out “Select Player” modal shows duplicates and wrong order. Make picker unique + sorted by position group + depth chart.

Requirements
- A player can only be selected once across ALL slots (Starting 15 + Subs).
- Picker must hide already-selected players.
- Picker order: GOALKEEPER, BACK, MIDFIELDER, FORWARD, then depthOrder asc (null last), then name.
- Picker UI grouped by position (SectionList headers).
- Unassigning (tap X) instantly makes the player reappear.
- Search applies AFTER filtering selected players.

Implementation (React Native + TS)

type Position="GOALKEEPER"|"BACK"|"MIDFIELDER"|"FORWARD";
type Player={id:string;name:string;primaryPosition:Position;depthOrder?:number|null};
type Slot={slot:number;playerId:string|null};

const POS_ORDER:Record<Position,number>={GOALKEEPER:0,BACK:1,MIDFIELDER:2,FORWARD:3};
const POS_LABEL:Record<Position,string>={GOALKEEPER:"Goalkeepers",BACK:"Backs",MIDFIELDER:"Midfielders",FORWARD:"Forwards"};

const getSelectedIds=(slots:Slot[])=>{
  const s=new Set<string>(); slots.forEach(x=>x.playerId&&s.add(x.playerId)); return s;
};

const buildSections=(players:Player[], selected:Set<string>, search:string)=>{
  const q=search.trim().toLowerCase();
  const avail=players
    .filter(p=>!selected.has(p.id))
    .filter(p=>!q||p.name.toLowerCase().includes(q))
    .sort((a,b)=>{
      const p=POS_ORDER[a.primaryPosition]-POS_ORDER[b.primaryPosition]; if(p) return p;
      const da=a.depthOrder??9999, db=b.depthOrder??9999; if(da!==db) return da-db;
      return a.name.localeCompare(b.name);
    });

  const g:{[K in Position]:Player[]}={GOALKEEPER:[],BACK:[],MIDFIELDER:[],FORWARD:[]};
  avail.forEach(p=>g[p.primaryPosition].push(p));
  return (Object.keys(g) as Position[])
    .map(pos=>({title:POS_LABEL[pos], data:g[pos]}))
    .filter(sec=>sec.data.length);
};

Screen wiring
- selectedIds = useMemo(() => getSelectedIds([...starting15,...subs]), [starting15,subs])
- sections = useMemo(() => buildSections(players, selectedIds, searchText), [players,selectedIds,searchText])
- Render SectionList with sections.

Actions
- onPick(player): setSlot(slotIndex, player.id), close modal.
- onUnassign(slotIndex): setSlot(slotIndex, null). Player returns automatically.
- Save guard: block save if any duplicate playerId exists across slots (server-side too).

Done when: picker never shows selected players, is grouped and depth-sorted, and unassign instantly restores availability.

